0ab8265a-7dcd-5d2a-8465-4b022474384f,tg:rubgr:1710,e73_Descriptions,,id.desc,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,"[recto] Good Shepherd. An Zwollo, Pieter Stevens, Ein vergessener Maler des rudolfinischen Kreises, Jh.d. Kh. Slgen in Wien [= Jahrbuch der kunsthistorischen Sammlungen in Wien], Bd. 64 (Neue Folge Bd XXVIII) 1968, pp. 119-180: a) important in connection with Franz's book; b) Good Shepherd fighting the Wolf, painting in Graz, Landesmuseum Joanneum, repr. p. 121, fig. 164, text p. 127 [...]; [toegevoegde vermelding]: 'F.G. Christ in left corner attacking the wolf who has seized a white lamb. The attitude of Christ similar to that in the 'Cornelis Massys' formerly with Harris; [verso] but Christ has a hat on his back (in contrast to Bruegel's Unfaithful shepherd who loses his hat. In both cases Christ is the Good Shepherd. The dying shepherd also approaches Christ in his features He says in John 10, 14 I am the Good Shepherd.",descriptive note,Nederlands,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,

column4: <content>[recto] Good Shepherd. An Zwollo, Pieter Stevens, Ein vergessener Maler des rudolfinischen Kreises, Jh.d. Kh. Slgen in Wien [= Jahrbuch der kunsthistorischen Sammlungen in Wien], Bd. 64 (Neue Folge Bd XXVIII) 1968, pp. 119-180: a) important in connection with Franz's book; b) Good Shepherd fighting the Wolf, painting in Graz, Landesmuseum Joanneum, repr. p. 121, fig. 164, text p. 127 [...]; [toegevoegde vermelding]: 'F.G. Christ in left corner attacking the wolf who has seized a white lamb. The attitude of Christ similar to that in the 'Cornelis Massys' formerly with Harris; [verso] but Christ has a hat on his back (in contrast to Bruegel's Unfaithful shepherd who loses his hat. In both cases Christ is the Good Shepherd. The dying shepherd also approaches Christ in his features He says in John 10, 14 I am the Good Shepherd.</content>
